title: Empty Promises
itunes:title: Empty Promises
description:
Dear Shirley Strawberry, I've been dating this guy's whole lot of empty promises. I let him in my life. He had potential. Nice looking, in school recently obtained his master's, hard working at one time held down two jobs, had his own place. At one time I had the key. Then along comes a BFF a best friend forever from New Jersey and he took the key back and then they move in to a 2 bedroom apartment......
